values.inter-word:
The text is justified by adding space between words (effectively varying
<a href="$MDN_URL$/Web/CSS/word-spacing"><code>word-spacing</code></a>
), which is most appropriate for languages that separate words using spaces, like English or Korean.

values.inter-character:
The text is justified by adding space between characters (effectively varying
<a href="$MDN_URL$/Web/CSS/letter-spacing"><code>letter-spacing</code></a>
), which is most appropriate for languages like Japanese.
